  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you reach 10th level, you achieve a profound understanding of how to use and make magic items:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You can <strong>attune </strong>to up to <strong>four </strong>magic items at once.</li>\n<li>If you craft a magic item with a rarity of <strong>common </strong>or <strong>uncommon</strong>, it takes you a quarter of the normal time, and it costs you half as much of the usual gold.</li>\n</ul>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: Foundry does not enforce maximum attunements, but you can edit the maximum at the bottom-left of the character's Inventory tab.</em></p>\n</section>",
